| Bespoke design | Dark execution console; Inter + DM Mono; palette from plan; NOT portfolio colors |
| WebGPU fallback | Mock mode with 6 canned responses (2 per engine, rotated by runCount) |

---

## Key Decisions

- **Main thread CreateMLCEngine** (no 13th worker file; stays within 12-file cap)
- **WebLLM pinned to 0.2.84** with auto-fallback to unpinned latest if model not found on init
- **VRAM detection via adapterInfo description**: integrated GPU signal triggers FALLBACK_MODEL (3B)
- **Canned responses**: 2 per engine, rotated by runCount modulo so repeated runs vary
- **Push gating**: `btn-push` rendered `disabled` + `title="Approve output first"` at card-build time; enabled only in `approveOutput()` callback - no code path bypasses this
- **Revision**: full re-run via reviseLLM(); new output record created (revised status); old output preserved in DB
- **All em/en dashes removed** via post-build perl pass; verified 0 remaining

